    "transcript": "The INEC data leak has raised urgent questions about how secure Nigerians’ personal information truly is in a digital democracy.\n\nIn this report, we examine what was exposed, why it matters, and how it connects to Nigeria’s broader and ongoing privacy challenges.\n\nFrom voter data protection to institutional accountability, this story goes beyond a single incident and into a national conversation about trust, technology, and governance.\n\nFollow ClearPath Media as we track the issues shaping Nigeria’s democracy and connect the ballot to your daily life.\n\n#INEC #dataleak  #nigeriapolitics  #PrivacyCrisis #datasecurity  #electionwatch  #clearpathmedia  #democracywatch  #nigeria2027  #cybersecurity  #governance",
